  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Travellin Cats in Japan (formerly Cats Hidden in Japan) is a cute hidden object game set in Japan.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100 cats are waiting for you to be discovered within a hand-drawn background.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relax thanks to the chill soundtrack</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Found a cat? Click on it!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🐾 1 Level </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >😺 100 cats</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌈 Color Mode</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > ❔ Easter Eggs</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 💡 Hint System</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌙 Night Mode</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >☀️ Adjustable Brightness</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⏰ Timer mode with leaderboard</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎨 Adjustable background & cats color</p>",
